                    (photocopy or scan) <br><br>- 01 copy of high school transcript (photo or scan) <br><br>- 01 copy of
                    ID card (photocopy or scan) <br><br>- 02 photos 3Ã—4 <br><br>- Certificate of English (if any)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>What majors does Greenwich Vietnam train?</th>
                <td> Currently, Greenwich Vietnam trains the following specialties: <br><br>- Information technology
                    industry <br><br>- Major in Business Administration with 4 narrow majors: Business Administration,
                    Marketing Management, Event Management, Communication Management<br><br>- Graphic Design Industry
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Where is the school headquarters located?</th>
                <td>- The campus of the University of Greenwich is located in London, UK. <br><br>- In Vietnam,
                    Greenwich Vietnam has 4 locations. For information about 4 facilities, candidates can refer to:
                    https://greenwich.edu.vn/lien-he/</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Does the school have dormitories for students?</th>
                <td>The school does not have a dormitory for students. If students have needs, the school will assist in
                    finding accommodation for students.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>My English is not good, can I study at Greenwich Vietnam?</th>
                <td>- Studying at Greenwich Vietnam, students will be guided and trained to improve their English.
                    First,
                    students will be directed to register and check their current English level assessment. The English
                    preparatory stage has 5 levels, each level is a different level according to the level of increase.
                    Depending on their level, students can shorten their preparatory English study time. <br><br>- Most
                    students of the program's courses go through the preparatory English phase without too much
                    difficulty. The teachers in the school with scientific teaching methods and the environment of using
                    English like a native help students improve their English quickly.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
